<sub>
    This is the Log of your journeys! Here is a list of all the quests you are currently on. You can view tips on how to complete an active
    quest by clicking the Help button on the top right corner of the quest entry. You can also view completed quests by clicking view all.
</sub>
{% for quest in QUESTS %}
    {{ quest.name }} - {{ quest.description }}<br/>
    {{ quest.task }}<br/>
    {% for i in 0..quest.stagecount %}
        {% if i==quest.stage %}
            <img height="24" src="http://img.drawnimals.com/quests/progress-current.png"/>
        {% elseif i < quest.stage %}
            <img height="24" src="http://img.drawnimals.com/quests/progress-done.png"/>
        {% else %}
            <img height="24" src="http://img.drawnimals.com/quests/progress-next.png"/>
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}<br/>
{% endfor %}